  "instructions": [
    "In a medium saucepan, heat sesame oil over medium heat.",
    "Add grated carrots and cook until tender, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add bulgur, water, and soy sauce to the saucepan.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 15-20 minutes.",
    "Fluff cooked bulgur with a fork and stir in green onions.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
